{
  "stem": "19690.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think before we want to explore the possibility of immigration, I think I should go back to the beginning of 1938.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the beginning of 1938, I got sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At one point, it was suspected that I had measles, which I did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then I also got a cough and they decided that it was a mild case of whooping cough.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My parents were very concerned about this and lung damage is always a problem with this, especially in those days when there were no antibiotics.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it lasted for about a month.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after that, my doctor decided that I should go to Switzerland with my mother for an extended period and take salt baths there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the papers were requested and finally in August, we were able to leave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were supposed to be gone for three months and go to three different places.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The first place we went to was Davos, where we stayed at San Souci Hotel, which is no longer there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we-- I took the baths every day and we walked around the area and we had a wonderful vacation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When we got our passports, we also got my father's passport and he promised that he would come. 1938, in the summer was already a very difficult time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Austria had fallen to the Germans and Hitler was making all kinds of noises.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother kept calling home and my father kept saying, I can't leave the business, I can't leave the business.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was the time when they were trying to sell the business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "After a month, we went from Davos to [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Lugano ?] and stayed at a hotel there, also Sans Souci.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I took the baths there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
